$ System.Xml.XmlDocument (class)

`System.Xml.XmlDocument` derives from → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Xml/XmlNode[`System.Xml.XmlNode`] and represents
an → development/XML/DOM/nodes/document in memory.

{ Methods

